OUR PROMOTERS AND PROMOTER GROUP

Jacob Joseph George, Mathew Chandy, Mathew George and Mathew Antony Joseph are the Promoters of our Company.

As on date of this Draft Red Herring Prospectus, our Promoters, in aggregate, hold 63,536,112 Equity Shares of face value of ₹1 each in our Company, representing 66.10% of the pre-Offer issued, subscribed and paid-up Equity Share capital of our Company on a fully diluted basis.
